notification_icon: Replace libappindicator usage with StatusNotifier

This replaces all usage of both GTK3's StatusIcon and libappindicator's
tray icon with direct usage of the StatusNotifer DBus API.

This does result in some regressions:

- There is no longer a menu:
  This is because libdbusmenu is a problematic dependency, its dead, and tied
  to GTK3 while GTK4 is out.
- There is no longer any XEmbed support:
  This was bound to happen eventually. GTK4 removed this API and its not worth
  us bothering implementing X11 only APIs ourselves.
- The icon no longer works when ran uninstalled.

This also includes an unrelated change:

- Default to the symbolic status icon
